<br>
My Theory is, he calls mobs to his side if agro'd. I can't even walk in there without mobs running towards me from maestro, and even what appears to be full fledged 2nd floor mobs (OMG Imagine 2nd floor mobs running themsevles downstarts LOL!)<br>
<br>
Interestingly enough, his agro is a lot like AoW. Had 1 monk/SK FD, no fail message, but he continued to attack them, like AoW where if he is damaged by you he will not stop attacking. <br>
<br>
Has anyone else seen this mob? Or run into this? <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=19375"><img src="http://gladstone.uoregon.edu/~afeigens/peep.jpg" border=0></a>
